{"tid":1250354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[621] 賽後檢討，電筒戰術","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T05:00:29.000Z","uid":58104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89e08f021987cd153b4214061942840864e526dc","tid":1250354,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"發夢朋友去完話高火數電筒好有效，<br />\n<br />\n暫時發現功效如下：<br />\n1. 阻止警方採證，警方幾次拎cam出黎想拍底罪證比電筒照兩照發現影唔到野就收晒皮。<br />\n2. 協助人群focus罪案現場，e.g.尋晚有黑警混入，全程照住佢個樣，亦打燈方便大家影底同認住條契弟<br />\n3. 有鬼想影你你可以唔洗同佢講咁多，開強光mode照撚住佢，佢唔會影到野，亦唔需要同佢搶手機<br />\n4. 幫警犬保持冷靜，人被光照住會冷靜d<br />\n記得起咁多，諗到再補充。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人要活在光明裡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共勉之<br />\n<br />\n玩Laser我有保留，始終有傷害性，唔怕比警犬亂入罪可以照去，唔建議亦唔阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n補充多2樣，<br />\n1. 減少現場黑暗死角位，防止暗角打獲<br />\n2. 絕對係有效自衛既方法之一，詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Emz_1HsKmn8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEmz_1HsKmn8&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=62030ca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Emz_1HsKmn8</a><br />\n來源：<br />\n我想問下咩叫戰術電筒?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n另外補充多條片，大家可以睇下鏡頭被照既效果:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Olw6XDA7dOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOlw6XDA7dOo&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=f9016fd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Olw6XDA7dOo</a><br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n發覺電筒都幾好用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1220940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1220940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n另外，屋企咁岩有把電筒幾好用可以介紹比大家(淘寶)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.tb.cn/h.e57BSFV?sm=52666d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.tb.cn%2Fh.e57BSFV%3Fsm%3D52666d&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=91136137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.tb.cn/h.e57BSFV?sm=52666d</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n提多樣野，發夢尋晚個朋友話有記者行埋去同佢講叫佢照高少少，有幾次都妨礙左記者拍攝，我地同記者絕對係同一陣線(cctvb除外)，已經即場道歉，並表示絕對無意妨礙記者。<br />\n<br />\n如果玩，大家都記得要注意避開記者鏡頭。互相體諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6c8e8b43682c5466162e65fbd3714163e70602","tid":1250354,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"希望推比多d人見到，親身證實的確好有用，特別如果預料會有夜間行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}